Our Vision and Mission

Google Developer Group (GDG) Kolkata is a community-based focused group for developers on Google and related technologies.

We as a community, organize various events on Google Products and the latest development technologies and platforms. Our aim is to establish and grow an open community of student and professional developers who are passionate about technology, allowing them to learn, share, and collaborate among themselves. We are working towards that goal through various events such as the ones below.



DevFest

The biggest Google related event in the country carefully crafted for you by GDG community! Awesome speakers and lots of fun!

I/O Extended

Community meetup to dive deeper and discuss about the latest announcements at Google I/O.
